{"tid":2190725,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美總統國安顧問：中國有干預美國選舉的最大規模計畫","createTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T02:49:29.000Z","uid":294518,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"48ff625f9b7c12ca57f74fe0484b8b28809cfadd","tid":2190725,"uid":294518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T02:48:05.000Z","msg":"奧布萊恩告訴記者稱，&ldquo;我們知道中國擔當最積極的角色&rdquo;，並提到&ldquo;中國有最龐大的計畫，從政治方面影響美國，其次是伊朗和俄羅斯&rdquo;。他指出，美國已很清楚地告訴中國、俄羅斯、伊朗和其他國家，任何干預美國大選的企圖將面臨嚴重後果。<br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩8月間曾聲稱，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">中國駭客對美國選舉的基礎設施發功了攻擊。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n奧布萊恩回應指，&ldquo;我不會討論所有這些情報問題，中國方面以及網絡領域的大量活動，真的是我<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\">們面臨的一件不同尋常的事情。&rdquo;他稱，&ldquo;我們從來沒有看過類似的事情。跟蘇聯的冷戰情況也不是這樣。&rdquo;</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200905-%E7%BE%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rfi.fr%2Ftw%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%2F20200905-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E9%25A1%25A7%25E5%2595%258F-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25B9%25B2%25E9%25A0%2590%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589%25E7%259A%2584%25E6%259C%2580%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25A6%258F%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmRyWBa%2BgBXVTVyFCVgu0cTpM%3D&h=ea8b854c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.rfi.fr/tw/%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB/20200905-%E7%BE%8E%E7%B8%BD%E7%B5%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E9%A1%A7%E5%95%8F-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%89%E5%B9%B2%E9%A0%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89%E7%9A%84%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%A7%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB</a><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部長巴爾（William Barr）2日在接受美國有線電視新聞網（CNN）採訪時表示，&ldquo;在外國勢力干預美國總統大選方面，